title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker

lines.text: At last. (Ren seems uneasy. He walks through the darkness. Lightning shows the room is filled with gigantic statues from Sith leaders.) Snoke trained you well.
I killed Snoke. I'll kill you.
My boy. I made Snoke. (when Kylo stands still) I have been every voice (as Snoke) you have ever heard (as Darth Vader) inside your head.
The First Order was just the beginning. I will give you so much more.

I have died before. (The leader of the First Order turns his head and steps towards the voice) The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some consider to be (Lightning illuminates his face) unnatural.

Everything. (He spreads his mangled fingers. Force lightning sparkles between them) A new Empire. (The Imperial March makes itself heard as a massive fleet of Star Destroyers break through the icy surface of Exegol) The might of the Final Order will soon be ready. s a mole in the First Order, and they sent us a message.
